                        <span class="bg-warning text-dark rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fw-black shadow-sm" style="width: 22px; height: 22px; font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer;">?</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
